# Prototype Validation

1. Components depend on domain contracts, not `src/generated/**`
2. Mock providers satisfy the same contracts real providers will
3. Do not add connectors until the planning payload is stable
4. Use `dataverse/prototype-feedback.md` to capture findings
5. Feed findings back into `dataverse/planning-payload.json`
6. Promote from prototype to schema only when the UX stops forcing schema changes

Full details: `.github/instructions/00d-prototype-validation.instructions.md`
